  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/fb12ef081a66f7c178bd8b11805e03ef.avif?t=1692378518\" width=640 height=407 /></span><br><br>Dotto Botto is a classic Super Mario Bros. platformer game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/44dde80ffc14c89153f3a1de0bb70796.poster.avif?t=1692378518\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/44dde80ffc14c89153f3a1de0bb70796.webm?t=1692378518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/44dde80ffc14c89153f3a1de0bb70796.mp4?t=1692378518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Help Dotto to find his way home and try to beat all the levels!<br><br>You will face deadly enemies, weird creatures and hideous obstacles on your way back home, so be careful!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/6b64291e69d39c4e58bf3450892003c0.avif?t=1692378518\" width=64 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/d7ffe92dd80061a429567d4ec0ecfbad.poster.avif?t=1692378518\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/d7ffe92dd80061a429567d4ec0ecfbad.webm?t=1692378518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/d7ffe92dd80061a429567d4ec0ecfbad.mp4?t=1692378518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>10 Levels full of moving platforms, obstacles, power-ups, spikes, enemies and much more! (not so much more, actually)<br>2 game endings! (yes, not 1 but 2!!!! unbelievable!!!)<br>Colorful pixelated graphics<br>Both Gamepad and Keyboard supported<br>A monstrous Final Boss!<br>4 Different enemies<br>Dozens of traps and obstacles!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/53a779297e38e6f5ed15068b30e169c3.poster.avif?t=1692378518\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/53a779297e38e6f5ed15068b30e169c3.webm?t=1692378518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912660/extras/53a779297e38e6f5ed15068b30e169c3.mp4?t=1692378518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Controls</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gamepad</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >D-pad Or Left-stick = Move</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A / B = Jump / Skip Intro / Select</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Start / Back = Pause Game</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wasd Or Arrow Keys = Move/ Jump</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spacebar  = Skip Intro/ Jump / Select</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >P / Esc = Pause Game</h2>",
